---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
  title: "Privacy Policy | ReviByte Opinion",
  description: "Transparent privacy practices at ReviByte Opinion – we collect almost nothing, never sell your data, and put your trust first."
};
---

<BaseLayout meta={meta}>
  <article class="prose prose-lg mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-16 dark:prose-invert">
    <header class="text-center">
      <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-bold">Privacy Policy – ReviByte Opinion</h1>
      <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
        We value your privacy. This document explains what data we collect (very little), why, and how it’s used.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        Last updated: December 2025
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2">
        Questions? Email us at 
        <a href="mailto:hello@revibyte.online" class="font-semibold text-blue-600 hover:underline">
          hello@revibyte.online
        </a>
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="my-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-50 p-8 dark:bg-blue-950/30">
      <h2 class="mb-4 flex items-center text-2xl font-bold">
        Quick Summary
      </h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-lg">
        <li>• We do <strong>not sell</strong> your personal information.</li>
        <li>• We use minimal cookies (only for basic functionality and ads).</li>
        <li>• Some data is collected automatically (IP, device info, pages visited).</li>
        <li>• You can request deletion or opt out of personalized ads anytime.</li>
        <li>• This site complies with GDPR, CCPA, COPPA, and advertising policies.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>1. What Information Do We Collect?</h2>
    <p><strong>We collect only the minimum information needed to run the site.</strong></p>

    <h3>Automatically Collected Data</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>IP address (may be anonymized depending on your region)</li>
      <li>Device type, operating system, and browser</li>
      <li>Pages viewed, time spent, and referral source</li>
      <li>Advertising identifiers (Google AdSense cookies, if ads are active)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>If You Contact Us or Comment</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Name and email address you provide</li>
      <li>Your message or comment content</li>
    </ul>

    <p>We do <strong>not collect</strong> passwords, payment details, or sensitive personal data.</p>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To operate and maintain the website</li>
      <li>To understand visitor engagement and improve content</li>
      <li>To display relevant advertisements (via Google AdSense, if enabled)</li>
      <li>To reply to your emails or support requests</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Cookies & Advertising</h2>
    <p>This site may use cookies from:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Google Analytics (for understanding traffic)</li>
      <li>Google AdSense / Advertising partners</li>
    </ul>

    <p>These help show relevant ads and improve user experience.</p>

    <p class="mt-6">
      <strong>Manage or disable personalized ads:</strong><br/>
      <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn">
        Google Ad Preferences
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.youradchoices.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn ml-3">
        AdChoices Opt-Out
      </a>
    </p>

    <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your location (EU, UK, California, etc.), you have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access your personal data</li>
      <li>Request corrections or deletion</li>
      <li>Receive a copy of your data (portability)</li>
      <li>Opt out of personalized advertising</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Just email 
      <a href="mailto:hello@revibyte.online?subject=Privacy Request">
        hello@revibyte.online
      </a> — I handle all requests personally within 48 hours.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p>ReviByte Opinion is not intended for users under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

    <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Analytics data: up to 26 months</li>
      <li>Emails/messages: kept only as long as needed</li>
      <li>Ad data: controlled by Google</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>7. Security</h2>
    <p>We use HTTPS encryption and rely on secure third-party platforms (Google, Astro hosting) to protect any stored data.</p>

    <h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We’ll update this page if anything changes. The “Last updated” date at the top will always reflect the latest version.</p>

    <p class="mt-16 text-center text-lg italic text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      Thank you for trusting <strong>ReviByte Opinion</strong> with your time — and your privacy.<br><br>
      — <strong>Oke "iSamuel"</strong>, Founder
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
